  <summary>2/4/1997--Introduced.
Free Market Grazing Fees Act - Directs the Secretaries of Agriculture and the Interior to establish fair market value grazing fees for use of their respective public lands. Establishes a prevailing fee exception for current small family ranch leases or permits.</summary>
